The actual relationship between the three variables is simply formula_98 In other words, in this case formula_99 has one physically relevant root, and it is unity. The fact that only a single value of formula_93 will do and that it is equal to 1 is not revealed by the technique of dimensional analysis.

===The simple pendulum===
